                            <comment id="17275750" author="marett" created="Sun, 31 Jan 2021 01:04:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added a link to a unit and integration test that reproduce the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17275751" author="marett" created="Sun, 31 Jan 2021 01:10:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added a client workaround to make the IT test pass. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17276284" author="kwin" created="Mon, 1 Feb 2021 12:11:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=marett&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;marett&quot;&gt;marett&lt;/a&gt; Thanks for the report, can you come up with a fix?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17276622" author="marett" created="Mon, 1 Feb 2021 20:06:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=kwin&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;kwin&quot;&gt;kwin&lt;/a&gt; sure, I have opened PR &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/pull/121&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;#121&lt;/a&gt;&#160;which contains the tests and a fix.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;\Q&lt;/tt&gt; construct is documented in&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17277007" author="kwin" created="Tue, 2 Feb 2021 10:06:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/commit/f688495999147fb6438ec091e58b58aeba5e1365&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/commit/f688495999147fb6438ec091e58b58aeba5e1365&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17287066" author="marett" created="Fri, 19 Feb 2021 13:07:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=kwin&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;kwin&quot;&gt;kwin&lt;/a&gt;&#160;I just found out that the PR &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/pull/121&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;#121&lt;/a&gt; contained the workaround for tests from &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/tmaret/jackrabbit-filevault/commit/5e7ac66da9c92f4e8150e3a57c391e543e561474&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;5e7ac66da&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The PR &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/pull/123&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;#123&lt;/a&gt; removes the workaround from the test and will increase the test coverage of the fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17287067" author="marett" created="Fri, 19 Feb 2021 13:10:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dsuess&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dsuess&quot;&gt;dsuess&lt;/a&gt; for pointing me to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/runs/1815540229&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/runs/1815540229&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
